# Frozen UI decisions (do not revert)

Until the user explicitly asks to change these back:

1. **Calendar confirm / delete sheets** — Keep confirm and repeat-delete UI **inside** the EventSheet / Vaul drawer so taps work. Do not move them to `document.body` portals alone, and do not switch back to relying on `window.confirm` for those flows. Keep Select menus portaled into the sheet (`SelectContent` `container`).

2. **Live Activity Lock Screen copy** — Keep custom relative labels (`X時間Y分後` / `まもなく` / `予定時間になりました`). Do **not** switch back to `Text(timerInterval:)` style countdowns.

Related files: `src/components/EventSheet.tsx`, `src/components/ui/select.tsx`, `ios/App/EssentialsWidget/EssentialsWidgetLiveActivity.swift`.

Background / architecture: `docs/LIVE_ACTIVITY_DESIGN_AND_ISSUES.md`.
